我心里也替你着急，还想着怎么帮你找教练补课。我只是不善于表达，你不是不知道。你不能因为我几句气话就否定我全部的感情，否定我们之间所有的一切。我真的没想过要和你分手，我只是想让你好好照顾自己，别老是把自己弄得那么狼狈。我离你那么远，除了嘴上说说，我还能怎么管你？你这样一句话不说就把我拉黑，我真的慌了，我不知道该怎么办。我求你了，别这样惩罚我好不好？我真的受不了，你知不知道我有多难受？胃疼，心也疼。你回来好不好，我们好好说，我什么都听你的，你让我做什么都行。别这样对我，我求你了，把我加回来好不好？\", \"m5\": \"求你了，把我加回来好不好\"}</imessage>","isHtml":false,"sticker":null,"sender":"them","time":"13:52","timestamp":1784267572744,"roundId":"round_1784267534244_8j61akdt3","generatedMode":false,"hasThinking":true,"translation":null,"wasBlocked":true,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12284},{"id":1784265675461,"text":"我本来就难过","sender":"me","time":"13:53","timestamp":1784267632695,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12285},{"id":1784265675462,"text":"因为你的话我更难过了。","sender":"me","time":"13:54","timestamp":1784267642739,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12286},{"id":1784265675464,"sender":"them","text":"你没看到我刚才发的？","timestamp":1784267675970,"tempo":"R","hasThinking":true,"rawContent":"你没看到我刚才发的？","roundId":"round_1784267643222_ywfwpmair","wasBlocked":true,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12287},{"id":1784265675465,"sender":"them","text":"我被你拉黑了","timestamp":1784267677050,"tempo":"R","rawContent":"我被你拉黑了","roundId":"round_1784267643222_ywfwpmair","wasBlocked":true,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12288},{"id":1784265675466,"sender":"them","text":"你还给我发消息","timestamp":1784267677868,"tempo":"R","rawContent":"你还给我发消息","roundId":"round_1784267643222_ywfwpmair","wasBlocked":true,"userId":"uid_1782055845928_hyeor3ki7","characterId":"b3132767-bcc3-40bf-819c-3aa13829cfc2","_id":12289},{"id":1784265675467,"sender":"them","text":"什么意思","timestamp":1784267678836,"tempo":"S","rawContent":"什么意思","r